    <a href=\"../../szdw_/jsml.htm\">教师名录</a>\n                &gt;\n                正文\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix container\"><ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\">\n    \n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw_/szgk.htm\" title=\"师资概况\">师资概况</a></li>\n\n    \n    <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szdw_/jsml.htm\" title=\"教师名录\">教师名录</a></li>\n\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n  </div>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n\n<div class=\"clearfix\">\n<ul class=\"banner-ul pull-right tabs-ul clearfix\">\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n\n<div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n<div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/E/50/AC/7E2E94BE05E262A20F43E604DF4_33ABD066_8CBD.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>任罡</a>副研究员</div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                     \n                              \n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                \n               \n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n \n\n\n   \n    <div id=\"vsb_content\" class=\"wow fadeInUp sznr\"><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">个人介绍</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">姓名：任罡</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">职称：副研究员</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">邮箱：</span><a href=\"mailto:rengang@cernet.edu.cn\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">rengang@cernet.edu.cn</span></a></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">教育背景</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">工学博士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"> (</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">计算机科学与技术</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">), </span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">清华大学</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">中国</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">, 2009</span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">研究领域</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">下一代互联网体系结构及安全</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">真实IP源地址验证体系结构和关键技术</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">网络测量</span></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">研究概况</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">研究工作主要集中在下一代互联网体系结构及安全、真实IP源地址验证体系结构和关建技术，以及网络测量等领域。在真实IP源地址验证领域，共同提出下一代互联网真实源地址验证体系结构SAVA；在国际互联网标准化组织IETF推进成立SAVI工作组，执笔撰写中国在IETF第一个非Informational类别的国际标准RFC5210；参加团队从国家“十五”到“十四五”期间此领域的所有重要项目，并承担其中国家自然科学基金项目和国家实验室、国家重点研发计划子课题等；获得国家科技进步一等奖、中国电子学会特等奖、中国高校十大科技进展、教育部一等奖等荣誉。在下一代互联网体系结构及安全领域，承担中央网信办项目，设计下一代互联网安全相关体系；并为工信部、国家计算机网络应急技术处理协调中心等单位撰写IPv6安全相关方案和报告；长期讲授研究生专业课《下一代互联网及其安全》，共同撰写专著《下一代互联网》。在网络测量领域，重点研究IPv6活跃地址探测，包括有种子区域的探测优化，种子稀疏区域的探测，基于人工智能的探测等领域，成果多次在亚太互联网络信息中心APNIC会议上报告。</span></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">奖励与荣誉</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">1. 国家科学技术进步一等奖，下一代互联网源地址验证体系结构SAVA关键技术与规模化应用，吴建平、李星、李崇荣、刘莹、徐恪、任罡、尹霞、李贺武、徐明伟、崔勇、李丹、王继龙、解冲锋、顾钰楠、林涛，2024年颁发<br></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">2. 中国电子学会特等奖，下一代互联网真实源地址验证体系结构、关键技术与规模化应用，吴建平、毕军、李星、李崇荣、刘莹、徐恪、任罡、尹霞、李贺武、徐明伟、崔勇、李丹、解冲锋、顾钰楠、林涛，2020年<br></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">3. 教育部技术发明一等奖，互联网真实源地址验证关键技术及其应用，吴建平、毕军、李星、李崇荣、徐恪、任罡，2013年<br></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">4. 中国通信学会二等奖，支持IPv6源地址验证的交换机关键技术，毕军、胡萍、任罡、段海新、徐恪、王之梁、刘武、姚广、林萍萍、刘冰洋，2010年<br></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">5. 中国高等学校十大科技进展，下一代互联网核心技术国际标准RFC5210（IPv6真实源地址体系结构及测试床），吴建平、毕军、李星、任罡、徐恪，2008年<br></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">6. 第二届IPv6技术应用创新大赛科教赛道暨第七届下一代互联网技术创新大赛二等奖，基于实时模式生成和遗传算法优化的全球IPv6地址扫描系统，学生：张伟、杨昊翔，指导教师：任罡、尹霞、何林，2024年</span></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">学术成果</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p>代表性论文、国际标准、专著和会议报告<br></p>\n<p>1. Jianping Wu, Gang Ren, Xing Li，Source address validation: architecture and protocol design，ICNP 2007<br>2. Jianping Wu, Gang Ren, Xing Li，Building a next generation Internet with Source Address Validation Architecture, Science in China, Series F:Information Sciences，2008<br>3. Jianping Wu, Jun Bi, Xing Li, Gang Ren, Ke Xu, Mark Williams. A Source Address Validation Architecture (SAVA) testbed and deployment experiences. IETF RFC 5210，2008<br>4. 刘莹，吴茜，任罡，下一代互联网，电子工业出版社，2012<br>5. Ying Liu, Gang Ren*, Jianping Wu, Shenglin Zhang, Lin He, Yihao Jia, Building an IPv6 address generation and traceback system with NIDTGA in Address Driven Network, SCIENCE CHINA-Information Sciences. 2015<br>6. Yihao Jia,Ying Liu, Gang Ren*, Lin He，Revisiting inter-AS IP Spoofing Let the Protection Drive Source Address Validation, IPCCC，2017<br>7. Yihao Jia, Ying Liu, Gang Ren*，Lin He，RISP: A RPKI-Based Inter-AS Source Protection Mechanism，Tsinghua Science and Technology,2018<br>8. Lishan Li, Gang Ren, Ying Liu and Jianping Wu，Secure DHCPv6 Mechanism for DHCPv6 Security and Privacy Protection，Tsinghua Science and Technology，2018<br>9. Ying Liu, Lin He, Gang Ren*，GAGMS: a requirement-driven general address generation and management system, SCIENCE CHINA-Information Sciences，2018<br>10. Lin He, Gang Ren, Ying Liu. Bootstrapping Accountability and Privacy to IPv6 Internet without Starting from Scratch, INFOCOM 2019<br>11. Yihao Jia, Ying Liu, Gang Ren*，Address Protection-as-a-Service：An inter-AS Framework for IP Spoofing Resilience，GLOBECOM 2019<br>12. Lishan Li, Ying Liu, Jianping Wu, Gang Ren，GSDM: Graph-based Scaling Detection Model in Network Function Virtualization，GLOBECOM 2019<br>13. Lishan Li, Ying Liu, Jianping Wu, Gang Ren，NFVMP: An Architecture for NFV Applications from Multiple Providers，APNOMS 2019（Best Paper Award）<br>14. Lin He, Peng Kuang, Ying Liu, Gang Ren, Jiahai Yang, Towards Securing Duplicate Address Detection Using P4, Computer Networks, 2021<br>15. Lin He, Gang Ren, Ying Liu, Jiahai Yang. PAVI: Bootstrapping Accountability and Privacy to IPv6 Internet, IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 2021<br>16. Lin He, Gang Ren, Ying Liu, Guanglei Song, Jinlong E, Jiahai Yang, and Mingwei Xu，SAV6: A Novel Inter-AS Source Address Validation Protocol for IPv6 Internet，IEEE Network，2022<br>17. Wei Zhang, Gang Ren，Xia Yin, Lin He，Comprehensive measurement of IPv6 address interface identifier pattern in current IPv6 deployment, APNIC 58，2024<br>18. Xinzhe Liu, Yahui Li, Han Zhang, Xia Yin, Xingang Shi, Zhiliang Wang, Gang Ren, Jiangyuan Yao，Scalable and Interpretable Multilayer Overlay Network Checking via Ensemble Verification，SIGCOMM Poster，2024<br>19. Wei Zhang, Gang Ren, Xia Yin, Lin He. Analysis of IPv6 Adoption in Different Perspectives and a case study with BitTorrent，APNIC 59，2025<br>20. Gang Ren, Shuqi Liu, Xia Yin，Inter-domain Source Address Validation based on AS relationships，IETF draft，2025</p></div></div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n    </form>\n\n<style>\n.article-txt p,.article-txt p span {\n    font-size: 17px!important;}\n</style>\n<script>\n$(\"div>table,p>table\").each(function(){\n    if(!$(this).parent().is(\"vsbcontent-table-container\")){\n    $(this).wrap('<div class=\"vsbcontent-table-container-outer\"><div class=\"vsbcontent-table-container\"></div></div>');\n    }\n});\n</script>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n  <div class=\"footer wow fadeInUp\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"friends-box wow fadeInUp\"><div class=\"friends-left\">友情链接</div>\n    <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"清华大学\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1841579642, 82002)\">清华大学</a><span>/</span>\n    <a href=\"https://www.itc.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"信息化技术中心\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1841579642, 82003)\">信息化技术中心</a><span>/</span>\n    <a href=\"https://www.cs.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1841579642, 81621)\">计算机科学与技术系</a><span>/</span>\n    <a href=\"https://www.ee.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"电子工程系\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1841579642, 82005)\">电子工程系</a><span>/</span>\n    <a href=\"https://www.ias.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"高等研究院\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1841579642, 82006)\">高等研究院</a>\n</div>\n\n      <div class=\"clearfix wow fadeInUp footer_b\">\n        <div class=\"foot_l\">                            <a href=\"../../index.htm\" title=\"清华大学网络科学与网络